    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving powerplant delivers a linear torque curve through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis maintains factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a pristine suspension geometry that ensures razor-sharp turn-in. An unmolested, collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
